  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eat Colors is a precision platformer game where instead of running and jumping, you fling yourself from surface to surface, and you are a cute slime that sticks to anything.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772180/extras/d6e122a57cc323d2d1540a3cf43869ec.poster.avif?t=1742561311\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772180/extras/d6e122a57cc323d2d1540a3cf43869ec.webm?t=1742561311\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772180/extras/d6e122a57cc323d2d1540a3cf43869ec.mp4?t=1742561311\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mechanic</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >STAYING STILL COULD COST YOU YOUR LIFE!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to staying still, jumping in the same spot or trying to make long jumps can kill you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772180/extras/f7a8f6f87c55d1620e0e6503fa5f9f56.poster.avif?t=1742561311\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772180/extras/f7a8f6f87c55d1620e0e6503fa5f9f56.webm?t=1742561311\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772180/extras/f7a8f6f87c55d1620e0e6503fa5f9f56.mp4?t=1742561311\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging Gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battles against big enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >45 levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cute Slime</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >THINK, AIM, AND JUMP BEFORE IT'S TOO LATE!</p>",
